Thanks to David Raufeisen for this post:
http://mail.gnome.org/archives/gtk-list/2000-January/msg00072.html
which helped me learn how to make a gtk+ dockapp.

Thanks to wbk <coydog@coydogsoftware.net> for the suggestion to add an argument
for not storing the notes.

Thanks to Moritz <thinksilicon@users.sf.net> for a patch to properly set the
wmhints for the icon window.

Thanks to Doug Torrance <dtorrance@monmouthcollege.edu> for creating a man page
and for patches to fix the icon window size and to add some failure checks.

Thanks to Andreas Tscharner <andy@vis.ethz.ch> for suggesting the ability to
restore notes to previous workspaces and for pointing out a bug.

